snippet.title: Star Fox Adventures: Amethyst Edition Demo
snippet.description:
After months of collaboration and work, RenaKunisaki has released a playable Krystal mod for Star Fox Adventures, along with dozens of other quality-of-life and debugging features.

More improvements to come in the future. Find out more at http://segment6.net/sfa/amethyst
